## PFLICHT: `clients_view_model_territories` — Spezifische Anti-Regression-Checks

Bei JEDER Migration die `model_agency_territories` Policies berührt:

```sql
-- Check 1: Kein Self-Reference-Alias in irgendeiner Policy der Tabelle
SELECT count(*) FROM pg_policies
WHERE tablename = 'model_agency_territories'
  AND (qual ILIKE '%self_mat%'
    OR qual ILIKE '%from public.model_agency_territories%'
    OR qual ILIKE '%from model_agency_territories %');
-- Erwartet: 0

-- Check 2: clients_view_model_territories existiert als SELECT-Policy
SELECT policyname, cmd FROM pg_policies
WHERE tablename = 'model_agency_territories'
  AND policyname = 'clients_view_model_territories'
  AND cmd = 'SELECT';
-- Erwartet: 1 Zeile
```

